  "2320400": {
    "name": "Darkzan Arena",
    "steam_appid": 2320400,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/4d09c4fa7b2872a14fa7716a4cea4d52.avif?t=1748471641\" width=612 height=96 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>挑战传奇，击败怪物，称霸竞技场！</strong> 🔥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备迎接一场前所未有的史诗级挑战！在这个<strong>令人惊叹的竞技场</strong>中，挑战多元宇宙中最强大的传奇和怪物。收集稀有宝藏，升级装备，踏上成为<strong>史上第一</strong>的道路！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/6bcef40da85576d0bbb46a8dfbe29205.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/6bcef40da85576d0bbb46a8dfbe29205.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/6bcef40da85576d0bbb46a8dfbe29205.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>无尽的动作体验</strong>：一款街机风格的游戏，通过无尽的独特敌人波次挑战你的极限，每个敌人都有不可预测的行为和独特奖励！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>高级战斗系统</strong>：策略与技巧是胜利的关键！经验、伤害和耐力结合在一起，为你带来逐步进化的沉浸式游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>有趣且令人上瘾的进阶系统</strong>：每一次胜利，你都会变得更强大。流畅的系统确保每场游戏都能让你离巅峰更近一步。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌌 别再犹豫！证明你拥有称霸竞技场的实力，将你的名字载入多元宇宙的史册！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>💥 挑战已经发出，你准备好成为最强了吗？ 💥</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/73c495aa07de8cef1d7ba895192d4702.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/73c495aa07de8cef1d7ba895192d4702.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/73c495aa07de8cef1d7ba895192d4702.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>易于上手，难以精通！</strong> ⚔️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然游戏理念简单，但为追求极致的玩家提供了<strong>深度且富有挑战性的机制</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎯 <strong>可定制的战斗风格</strong>：尝试独特的攻击和技能组合，完全改变你的战斗策略。无论是灵活迅捷还是沉稳致命——风格由你决定，力量无可匹敌！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💡 <strong>无限可能，无尽乐趣</strong>：战斗的多样性允许每位玩家创造自己通往胜利的道路，尝试不同的方法克服挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>加入游戏，探索无尽的可能性！</strong> 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/2208101814ebc986c078eef8d115632b.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/2208101814ebc986c078eef8d115632b.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/2208101814ebc986c078eef8d115632b.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>⚔️ <strong>Darkzan 竞技场：这里没有规则——只有胜利！</strong> ⚔️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好迎接<strong>无限制的战斗</strong>！在<strong>Darkzan 竞技场</strong>，你携带的装备决定你的命运。选择你的武器：<strong>法杖、弓箭、剑</strong>或任何你能拿起的武器。只要你能携带，就能使用！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>无与伦比的力量</strong>：召唤术、死灵术、附魔武器、神秘书籍——<strong>你获得的一切都能用来击败敌人！</strong>掌握超乎想象的技能，成为传奇。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💎 <strong>数百种独特物品</strong>：从广泛的装备中选择，每件装备都有自己的特点、风格和毁灭性潜力。创建适合你战斗风格的组合，<strong>在竞技场上书写你的传奇！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏆 <strong>在 Darkzan 竞技场，唯一的限制是你的野心。你准备好超越所有人，成为不可战胜的吗？</strong> 🩸<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/c6d30a166c92e4bcef722cf2dd8e2719.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/c6d30a166c92e4bcef722cf2dd8e2719.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/c6d30a166c92e4bcef722cf2dd8e2719.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >⚔️ <strong>注意，挑战者：竞技场不会宽容！</strong> ⚔️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在<strong>Darkzan</strong>的竞技场中，你不会面对普通对手。这里汇聚了<strong>最强的强者</strong>，他们准备好证明自己配得上永恒的荣耀。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🔥 <strong>强大的法师</strong>：掌握奥术的高手，他们的魔法可以摧毁周围的一切。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏴‍☠️ <strong>传说中的海盗</strong>：快速的剑技、冷酷的策略以及遥不可及的宝藏光芒。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛡️ <strong>古代战士</strong>：带着古老战斗的怒火与智慧的老兵，渴望迎接新的挑战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >👁️ <strong>巅峰对手</strong>：每场战斗你都将面对技术巅峰的敌人，他们和你一样渴望登上顶峰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对面：你能击败这些无情的对手吗？还是成为众多失败者之一？</strong> 🌟</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>挑战在等待。证明你的力量吧！</strong> 💥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/ee0a27fa1df7bdbc5d13a30078403c45.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/ee0a27fa1df7bdbc5d13a30078403c45.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/ee0a27fa1df7bdbc5d13a30078403c45.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/21e0d1b89078a34c7ae48df22341da6c.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/21e0d1b89078a34c7ae48df22341da6c.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/21e0d1b89078a34c7ae48df22341da6c.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/1d7d3f526576f613b109d2277524b81e.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" width=640 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/1d7d3f526576f613b109d2277524b81e.webm?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/1d7d3f526576f613b109d2277524b81e.mp4?t=1748471641\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/f5e94a46e4a096436062ca0500d077ba.apng?t=1748471641\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320400/extras/f5e94a46e4a096436062ca0500d077ba.poster.avif?t=1748471641\" class=\"bb_img\" width=640 height=96 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
